\c 59
\s Munyengetero wekukumbira kununurwa pavavengi
\d Kumutungamiriri wekuimba. Aritasheti. Mikitani yaDhavhidhi. Sauro paakatuma, uye vakarinda imba kumuuraya.
\p
\v 1 Ndinunurei pavavengi vangu, Mwari wangu\x + Map. 143.9. 2 Sam. 22.49.\x*; ndiise pakakwirira kubva pane vanondimukira\x + Map. 143.9. 2 Sam. 22.49.\x*\x + Map. 17.7. 139.21.\x*.
\v 2 Ndinunurei kubva kuvaiti vezvakaipa\x + Map. 94.4.\x*, uye ndiponesei pavanhu veropa\x + Map. 5.6.\x*.
\p
\v 3 Nokuti tarirai, vanovandira mweya wangu\x + Map. 10.9.\x*; vane simba vakaunganira kundirwisa\x + Map. 56.6.\x*, pasina chitadzo changu uye pasina chivi changu, Jehovha\x + 1 Sam. 24.11. Map. 7.3.\x*.
\v 4 Vanomhanya nekuzvigadzira pasina mhosva\x + 1 Sam. 24.11. Map. 7.3.\x*; mukai, mundibatsire, muone\x + Map. 35.23.\x*.
\v 5 Naizvozvo imwi Jehovha Mwari wedzihondo, Mwari waIsraeri\x + Map. 80.4. 84.8.\x*, mukai kuti mushanyire vahedheni vese\x + Map. 35.23.\x*; musanzwira tsitsi umwe wevanyengeri pauipi. Sera\x + Map. 25.3.\x*.
\v 6 Vanodzoka madekwani, vanoita kuhuhudza seimbwa, ndokupoteredza guta\x + 59.14. Map. 22.16.\x*.
\v 7 Tarirai, vanodzvova nemiromo yavo\x + Map. 145.7.\x*, minondo iri pamiromo yavo\x + Map. 57.4.\x*, nokuti \add vanoti:\add* Ndiani anonzwa\x + Job. 22.13.\x*?
\v 8 Asi imwi Jehovha muchavaseka\x + Map. 2.4.\x*, muchatuka vahedheni vose\x + Map. 2.4.\x*.
\v 9 \add Nekuda kwe\add*simba rake ndichakurindirai; nokuti Mwari inhare yangu.
\v 10 Mwari wengoni dzangu achanditangira\x + Map. 21.3. Mat. 17.25.\x*, Mwari achandionesa \add chishuwo changu\add* pavavengi vangu\x + Map. 54.7.\x*.
\v 11 Musavauraya, zvimwe vanhu vekwedu vakanganwe, vadzungaidzei nesimba renyu\x + 59.15. Num.. 32.13. Gen.. 4.12-15.\x*, uye muvaburusire pasi\x + Map. 55.23. 56.7.\x*, imwi Jehovha\x + Map. 84.9.\x*, nhovo yedu.
\v 12 \add Ne\add*chivi chemuromo wavo, \add ne\add*shoko remiromo yavo\x + Zvir. 18.7.\x*, ngavabatwe pakuzvikudza kwavo, uye nekuda kwekunyomba nekutaura nhema dzavanorondedzera.
\v 13 \add Va\add*pedzei muhasha, \add va\add*pedzei vasavapo, kuti vazive kuti Mwari anotonga kwaJakove\x + Map. 83.18.\x* kusvika kumigumo yenyika. Sera\x + Map. 22.27.\x*.
\v 14 Zvino ngavadzoke pamadekwani, ngavahuhudze seimbwa, uye vapoteredze guta\x + 59.6.\x*.
\v 15 Ngavadzungairire kudya\x + 59.11. Map. 109.10. Job. 15.23.\x*; kana vasina kuguta ngavapedze usiku \add vachidaro\add*\x + Eki. 16.7. Num.. 16.11.\x*.
\p
\v 16 Asi ini ndichaimbira simba renyu; hongu ndichaimbira tsitsi dzenyu zvikuru mangwanani, nokuti manga muri nhare yangu\x + 59.9.\x* neutiziro pazuva\x + 2 Sam. 22.3.\x* rekutambudzika kwangu\x + Map. 66.14.\x*.
\v 17 Ndichakuimbirai nziyo dzekurumbidza, imwi simba rangu; nokuti Mwari ndiye nhare yangu yakakwirira\x + 59.9.\x*, Mwari wetsitsi dzangu\x + 59.10. Map. 144.2.\x*.